title: DDFP 593: AFC East Preview & could the Redskins win the NFC East?
itunes:title: DDFP 593: AFC East Preview & could the Redskins win the NFC East?
description:
Dave Dameshek and Matt Harmon rank the AFC East and determine if any team has a chance to unseat the New England Patriots as division leader. Then, Washington Redskins safety Will Blackmon joins the show to kibitz with Shek about the Game of Thrones finale, his love of wine and the 'Skins chances of winning the NFC East.
